<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pretend-v">pretend <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /prɪ'tend/    美 /prɪ'tend/  </p>
<p>vt &amp; vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>假装；装作：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What’s the good of pretending? 
装假有什么用呢？</p></div>

<ul>
<li>pretend to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When his mother came in, he pretended to be doing his homework. 
妈妈进来时，他假装在做作业。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>pretend (to sb) + that 从句:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He pretended to his family that everything was fine.
他对家人假装一切都好。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Miss Harper closed her eyes and <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ to be asleep.   （2010 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. pretended  </p></div>